0,"ip_address":"广东"},"score":2,"extra":"","child_discussion_number":0,"child_discussions":[]}]},{"had_liked":false,"id":68854,"user_name":"-Helen怪物","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c1","uid":1395364,"ip_address":"","ucode":"01D597BD9C15A8","user_header":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/15/4a/a4/7c5465b5.jpg","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1550623864,"is_pvip":false,"replies":[{"id":"24448","content":"嗯，篇幅所限，管理部分没像技术和业务部分一样展开。更细致的技术领导力，可以看刘建国老师的技术管理实战36讲。","user_name":"作者回复","comment_id":68854,"uid":"1173080","ip_address":"","utype":1,"ctime":1550630652,"user_name_real":"海飞"}],"discussion_count":1,"race_medal":0,"score":"27320427640","product_id":100023401,"comment_content":"文章对管理的理解，给了我提醒；但是我还是希望能获得更多对于管理的方法、能力、实践的讨论！","like_count":7,"discussions":[{"author":{"id":1173080,"avatar":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/11/e6/58/1c7f786a.jpg","nickname":"海飞","note":"","ucode":"C6B77418E1FB6D","race_medal":0,"user_type":2,"is_pvip":false},"reply_author":{"id":0,"avatar":"","nickname":"","note":"","ucode":"","race_medal":0,"user_type":1,"is_pvip":false},"discussion":{"id":439854,"discussion_content":"嗯，篇幅所限，管理部分没像技术和业务部分一样展开。更细致的技术领导力，可以看刘建国老师的技术管理实战36讲。","likes_number":0,"is_delete":false,"is_hidden":false,"ctime":1550630652,"is_liked":false,"can_delete":false,"is_complain":false,"is_top":true,"parent_id":0,"ip_address":""},"score":2,"extra":"{\"reply\":true,\"user_type\":2}","child_discussion_number":0,"child_discussions":[]}]},{"had_liked":false,"id":73848,"user_name":"Feng","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c1","uid":1019678,"ip_address":"","ucode":"4328C3CE24A8E3","user_header":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/0f/8f/1e/c7e77731.jpg","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1552015283,"is_pvip":false,"replies":[{"id":"27057","content":"谢谢分享。<br><br>稍微澄清一下，文中说的某个特质，并非那个职业方向独享，只不过比较而言，会更重要一点而已。<br><br>轮岗是个好方法，但是公司不一定允许。先把当前工作做好，然后基于当前工作，找找有没有关联到业务的工作，有倾向性的学习和接触下。当你表现出业务的能力时，老板就可以放心交给你更多业务内容的工作了。—— 还是要看你们公司的情况，允不允许这样的发展路子。","user_name":"作者回复","comment_id":73848,"uid":"1173080","ip_address":"","utype":1,"ctime":1552098366,"user_name_real":"海飞"}],"discussion_count":2,"race_medal":0,"score":"14436917171","product_id":100023401,"comment_content":"老师您好，这边重温这一章节的文字，个人收集到来自同事朋友的评价或者自身的职业人才测试，都偏向于业务；但是个人目前是技术岗位，对于问题会有好奇心，对事物保持新鲜感，但是更偏向于交互体验方面，技术是推动力，那么目前业务没有接触，基础不够的情况下，继续做技术，并且在过程中发展自己的综合能力是否是正确的选择呢，所有角色都很想像轮岗一样的，都体验一遍，迷茫的方向，体谅，同理心是个人测试出来的优势，但是没有找到那个准确的自我定位。与大家共勉","like_count":3,"discussions":[{"author":{"id":1173080,"avatar":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/11/e6/58/1c7f786a.jpg","nickname":"海飞","note":"","ucode":"C6B77418E1FB6D","race_medal":0,"user_type":2,"is_pvip":false},"reply_author":{"id":0,"avatar":"","nickname":"","note":"","ucode":"","race_medal":0,"user_type":1,"is_pvip":false},"discussion":{"id":442304,"discussion_content":"谢谢分享。\n\n稍微澄清一下，文中说的某个特质，并非那个职业方向独享，只不过比较而言，会更重要一点而已。\n\n轮岗是个好方法，但是公司不一定允许。先把当前工作做好，然后基于当前工作，找找有没有关联到业务的工作，有倾向性的学习和接触下。当你表现出业务的能力时，老板就可以放心交给你更多业务内容的工作了。—— 还是要看你们公司的情况，允不允许这样的发展路子。","likes_number":0,"is_delete":false,"is_hidden":false,"ctime":1552098366,"is_liked":false,"can_delete":false,"is_complain":false,"is_top":true,"parent_id":0,"ip_address":""},"score":2,"extra":"{\"reply\":true,\"user_type\":2}","child_discussion_number":0,"child_discussions":[]},{"author":{"id":1880460,"avatar":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/1c/b1/8c/8bd04e45.jpg","nickname":"米Venus","note":"","ucode":"377C1C3D313038","race_medal":0,"user_type":1,"is_pvip":false},"reply_author":{"id":0,"avatar":"","nickname":"","note":"","ucode":"","race_medal":0,"user_type":1,"is_pvip":false},"discussion":{"id":204926,"discussion_content":"首先我特别懂你，因为我就是这么做的，不知道你现在在什么岗位，还迷茫吗？分享一下个人的经历给你参考，轮岗未必是个好的选择。\n我从2010年到现在，1年自动化测试(技术)，1年手动测试(功能/UI/技术+业务)，1年半技术支持(技术运维，期间生了孩子)，然后4年产品反馈分析(技术+业务)，2年项目协调(管理)。\n最近又纠结自己的优势到底在哪里，直到细读白老师这两篇文章，发现我最想做的还是管理，从工作第二年就想做，只是各种机缘没有实现。而且做管理同时懂一些技术和业务也是更好的事，就释然了，明确了方向。如果早些明白，我不会到现在还是个项目协调员吧！\n所以我的个人建议还是早点定好方向，希望对你有所帮助。","likes_number":0,"is_delete":false,"is_hidden":false,"ctime":1584240251,"is_liked":false,"can_delete":false,"is_complain":false,"is_top":false,"parent_id":0,"ip_address":""},"score":2,"extra":"","child_discussion_number":0,"child_discussions":[]}]},{"had_liked":false,"id":275251,"user_name":"井中月","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c1","uid":1116945,"ip_address":"","ucode":"6C7A3951E0AD04","user_header":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/11/0b/11/b2283688.jpg","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1611410886,"is_pvip":false,"discussion_count":0,"race_medal":0,"score":"10201345478","product_id":100023401,"comment_content":"赤兔马这个梗，评论区居然没人点赞。","like_count":2},{"had_liked":false,"id":106514,"user_name":"Joseph","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c1","uid":1430073,"ip_address":"","ucode":"B7F6B88AB90679","user_header":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/15/d2/39/a7edf2b9.jpg","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1561338472,"is_pvip":false,"discussion_count":0,"race_medal":0,"score":"10151273064","product_id":100023401,"comment_content":"老师你好，目前的我是一名工作一年的后台开发，平时对技术是有一定的兴趣，但仅限于它给我带来的便捷性，除了硬性要求了解底层实现，不然也不会刨根问底。平时对业务也有了解，但是时间有限，平时有接触就认真学习。这样的习惯导致我好像啥都喜欢，但是并不精通一个领域，您觉得对于像我这类人，该怎么调整？","like_count":2},{"had_liked":false,"id":213587,"user_name":"高鹏0409","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c1","uid":1928337,"ip_address":"","ucode":"1833CA764B6A46","user_header":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/1d/6c/91/8268a753.jpg","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1588483766,"is_pvip":false,"discussion_count":0,"race_medal":0,"score":"5883451062","product_id":100023401,"comment_content":"后来人指着我的背影说，他变秃了，也变强了。","like_count":1},{"had_liked":false,"id":114569,"user_name":"我在时光机里找回忆","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c1","uid":1391450,"ip_address":"","ucode":"747081EF8AE506","user_header":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/15/3b/5a/4e3743e1.jpg","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1563340229,"is_pvip":false,"discussion_count":0,"race_medal":0,"